<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>自控力 on 布斯行</title><link>https://reading.wang/%E8%87%AA%E6%8E%A7%E5%8A%9B/</link><description>Recent content in 自控力 on 布斯行</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 23 Oct 2020 23:33:55 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://reading.wang/%E8%87%AA%E6%8E%A7%E5%8A%9B/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>吼呆时刻297-我不要的局限性</title><link>https://reading.wang/%E8%87%AA%E6%8E%A7%E5%8A%9B/2020-10-23-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB297-%E6%88%91%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%80%E9%99%90%E6%80%A7/</link><pubDate>Fri, 23 Oct 2020 23:33:55 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://reading.wang/%E8%87%AA%E6%8E%A7%E5%8A%9B/2020-10-23-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB297-%E6%88%91%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%80%E9%99%90%E6%80%A7/</guid><description>如果我们想要获得心灵的平静和足够的自控力，我们就需要认识到，控制自己的思想是件不可能的事。我们能做的就是，选择自己相信什么，选择自己要做什么。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻296-自控力会传染</title><link>https://reading.wang/%E8%87%AA%E6%8E%A7%E5%8A%9B/2020-10-22-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB296-%E8%87%AA%E6%8E%A7%E5%8A%9B%E4%BC%9A%E4%BC%A0%E6%9F%93/</link><pubDate>Thu, 22 Oct 2020 23:33:07 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://reading.wang/%E8%87%AA%E6%8E%A7%E5%8A%9B/2020-10-22-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB296-%E8%87%AA%E6%8E%A7%E5%8A%9B%E4%BC%9A%E4%BC%A0%E6%9F%93/</guid><description>质疑它的最好方法就是找到一群人，他们正在做你渴望做到的事。找到一个新的“群体”并加入进去。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻295-及时享乐?</title><link>https://reading.wang/%E8%87%AA%E6%8E%A7%E5%8A%9B/2020-10-21-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB295-%E5%8F%8A%E6%97%B6%E4%BA%AB%E4%B9%90/</link><pubDate>Wed, 21 Oct 2020 08:58:19 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://reading.wang/%E8%87%AA%E6%8E%A7%E5%8A%9B/2020-10-21-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB295-%E5%8F%8A%E6%97%B6%E4%BA%AB%E4%B9%90/</guid><description>我们会这么容易选择即刻的满足感，原因之一在于，我们大脑的奖励系统还没有进化到能对未来的奖励作出回应。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻294-情绪低落与诱惑</title><link>https://reading.wang/%E8%87%AA%E6%8E%A7%E5%8A%9B/2020-10-20-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB294-%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E4%BD%8E%E8%90%BD%E4%B8%8E%E8%AF%B1%E6%83%91/</link><pubDate>Tue, 20 Oct 2020 23:01:24 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://reading.wang/%E8%87%AA%E6%8E%A7%E5%8A%9B/2020-10-20-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB294-%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E4%BD%8E%E8%90%BD%E4%B8%8E%E8%AF%B1%E6%83%91/</guid><description>情绪低落为何会使人屈服于诱惑？</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻293-误把渴望当幸福</title><link>https://reading.wang/%E8%87%AA%E6%8E%A7%E5%8A%9B/2020-10-19-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB293-%E8%AF%AF%E6%8A%8A%E6%B8%B4%E6%9C%9B%E5%BD%93%E5%B9%B8%E7%A6%8F/</link><pubDate>Mon, 19 Oct 2020 07:11:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://reading.wang/%E8%87%AA%E6%8E%A7%E5%8A%9B/2020-10-19-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB293-%E8%AF%AF%E6%8A%8A%E6%B8%B4%E6%9C%9B%E5%BD%93%E5%B9%B8%E7%A6%8F/</guid><description>多巴胺控制的是行动，而不是快乐，奖励的承诺保证了被试者成功地行动，从而获得奖励。当奖励系统活跃的时候，他们感受到的是期待，而不是快乐。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻292-容忍罪恶</title><link>https://reading.wang/%E8%87%AA%E6%8E%A7%E5%8A%9B/2020-10-18-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB292-%E5%AE%B9%E5%BF%8D%E7%BD%AA%E6%81%B6/</link><pubDate>Sun, 18 Oct 2020 10:11:14 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://reading.wang/%E8%87%AA%E6%8E%A7%E5%8A%9B/2020-10-18-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB292-%E5%AE%B9%E5%BF%8D%E7%BD%AA%E6%81%B6/</guid><description>容忍罪恶：为何善行之后会有恶行？</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻291-自控力有极限</title><link>https://reading.wang/%E8%87%AA%E6%8E%A7%E5%8A%9B/2020-10-17-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB291-%E8%87%AA%E6%8E%A7%E5%8A%9B%E6%9C%89%E6%9E%81%E9%99%90/</link><pubDate>Sat, 17 Oct 2020 22:31:44 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://reading.wang/%E8%87%AA%E6%8E%A7%E5%8A%9B/2020-10-17-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB291-%E8%87%AA%E6%8E%A7%E5%8A%9B%E6%9C%89%E6%9E%81%E9%99%90/</guid><description>如果你想彻底改变旧习惯，最好先找一种简单的方法来训练自控力、提高意志力，而不是设定一个过高的目标。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻290-意志力的本能</title><link>https://reading.wang/%E8%87%AA%E6%8E%A7%E5%8A%9B/2020-10-16-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB290-%E6%84%8F%E5%BF%97%E5%8A%9B%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%AC%E8%83%BD/</link><pubDate>Fri, 16 Oct 2020 07:30:46 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://reading.wang/%E8%87%AA%E6%8E%A7%E5%8A%9B/2020-10-16-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB290-%E6%84%8F%E5%BF%97%E5%8A%9B%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%AC%E8%83%BD/</guid><description>你不可能真的消灭一个欲望，因为欲望在你的内心和身体里，没有办法自动消失。应激反应会让你面对最原始的欲望，而这正是你当下最不愿看到的。自控力需要另一种自救的方式，一种能对抗这种新威胁的方式。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻289-认识你自己</title><link>https://reading.wang/%E8%87%AA%E6%8E%A7%E5%8A%9B/2020-10-15-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB289-%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%86%E4%BD%A0%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1/</link><pubDate>Thu, 15 Oct 2020 07:16:42 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://reading.wang/%E8%87%AA%E6%8E%A7%E5%8A%9B/2020-10-15-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB289-%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%86%E4%BD%A0%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1/</guid><description>只有能意识到自己在做什么，才可能停下来。</description></item><item><title>吼呆时刻288-什么是意志力</title><link>https://reading.wang/%E8%87%AA%E6%8E%A7%E5%8A%9B/2020-10-14-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB288-%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%98%AF%E6%84%8F%E5%BF%97%E5%8A%9B/</link><pubDate>Wed, 14 Oct 2020 22:55:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://reading.wang/%E8%87%AA%E6%8E%A7%E5%8A%9B/2020-10-14-%E5%90%BC%E5%91%86%E6%97%B6%E5%88%BB288-%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%98%AF%E6%84%8F%E5%BF%97%E5%8A%9B/</guid><description>要想在需要“说不”时“说不”，在需要“说好”时“说好”，你还得有第三种力量：那就是牢记自己真正想要的是什么。</description></item></channel></rss>